  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Data Dictionary Change Notice - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">Data Dictionary Change Notice</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">DDCN</xref>
) is a notice of a change to the NHS Data Model and Dictionary which is not appropriate for 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">Data Coordination Board</xref>
 publication as an 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/information_standards_notice.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Information_Standards_Notice</xref>
, as the change does not relate to an individual standard.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">Data Dictionary Change Notices</xref>
 can be downloaded from: 
    <xref href="https://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/DDCNs/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Data Dictionary Change Notices</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
Further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">Data Dictionary Change Notices</xref>
 can be found on the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/nhs_data_model_and_dictionary_service.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">NHS_Data_Model_and_Dictionary_Service</xref>
 part of the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/media/746/Data-Dictionary-Change-Notice-guidance/pdf/ddcnguide"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Policies: Data Dictionary Change Notice guidance</xref>
.  </p>

